      before testing
    - many: add new `snap run` command
    - snappy: unexport snappy.Install and snappy.Overlord.{Un,}Install
    - many: add some shared testing helpers to snap/snaptest and to
      boot/boottest
    - rest-api: support to send apps per snap (LP: #1564076)

